---
title: Cal Smart Apple and Salmon Salad with Garlic Croutons
description: This elegant salad comes with all the tastiest toppings: warm caramelized apples, feta cheese, dried cranberries and garlic croutons plus a gorgeous piece of pan-seared salmon to turn this oh-so-easy salad into a meal.

